Critical Survey: Controladora Vuela Compania de Aviacion, S.A.B. de C.V. (VLRS) versus Allegiant Travel (ALGT)

					Posted by Samantha Guadardo on Jul 27th, 2017 // No Comments 


Tweet












Controladora Vuela Compania de Aviacion, S.A.B. de C.V. (NYSE: VLRS) and Allegiant Travel (NASDAQ:ALGT) are both transportation companies, but which is the superior business? We will contrast the two companies based on the strength of their dividends, analyst recommendations, risk, valuation, institutional ownership, earnings and profitabiliy. 
Profitability


