Controladora Vuela Compania de Aviacion, S.A.B. de C.V. currently has a consensus price target of $16.10, suggesting a potential upside of 17.60%. Allegiant Travel has a consensus price target of $160.64, suggesting a potential upside of 12.18%. Given Controladora Vuela Compania de Aviacion, S.A.B. de C.V.’s stronger consensus rating and  higher probable upside, research analysts plainly believe Controladora Vuela Compania de Aviacion, S.A.B. de C.V. is more favorable than Allegiant Travel.
